@node "usage" ""
 USAGE:

      Very easy.. just run as a normal maxs door using the '34' command.

      Doors:Pmenu/Pmenu 85

                        ^^
                        ||
                        ||
               This is the menu you
               want it to jump to if
               user is allowed.


  Pmenu also creates a log of entries successfull or not
  'Doors:Pmenu/Pmenu.log'           
@endnode

